Dr Rai, Amrit - Toronto - Downtown

Dr Amrit Rai is an Ophthalmologist practicing in Toronto - Downtown. An Ophthalmologist (aka Ophthalmology, Optho, Eye specialists) is a specialist in the branch of medicine concerned with the study and treatment of disorders and diseases of the eye. Ophthalmologists specialize in procedures such as: Cataracts surgery, Diabetic retinopathy, Glaucoma, Corneal surgery, Laser vision correction, Oculoplastic surgery.
